@@ -2,6 +2,15 @@
 
 All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
 
+## [0.7.0] - Phase 3.0 UI Polish
+- Added advanced multi-pane layout to Ratatui TUI.
+- Added view system with `/view <chat|tasks|repo|patches|tools|memory|skills|subagents|external|help>`.
+- Added command palette foundation with `/palette` and `/command`.
+- Improved task, workflow, subagent, and external agent display panels.
+- Keyboard shortcuts added (`Ctrl+1` through `Ctrl+9` for views, `Ctrl+P` for palette).
+- Graceful fallback to single-pane layout on narrow terminals.
+- Retained ApprovalGate, tools, headless mode, and all backend workflows intact.
+
 ## [0.6.0] - Phase 2 Framework Complete
 - Added `ExternalAgentManager` with secure workspace isolation (`isolated-copy`).
 - Added jsonl audit logging for remote execution.
